<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٨٧١ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3902">عَبْدُ اللهِ بْنُ مُحَمَّدٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6244">مُعَاوِيَةُ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/96">أَبُو إِسْحَاقَ </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1647">حُمَيْدٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسًا </a><span class="special">﵁</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«كَانَتْ نَاقَةُ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> يُقَالُ لَهَا الْعَضْبَاءُ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>